analysis: The deployment of the Knowage-Server application encountered multiple issues primarily due to missing or misconfigured files. feedback: The deployment failed due to missing or misconfigured files. Ensure that the project structure aligns with the expected files for the Knowage-Server application. Verify the presence of necessary startup files and commands in the project documentation before attempting deployment.
